  "original_title": "\u0da9\u0dd3\u0dc3\u0dbd\u0dca \u0dc4\u0dd2\u0d9f\u0dba\u0da7 \u0dad\u0dc0\u0db8\u0dad\u0dca \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0db3\u0dd4\u0db8\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db1\u0dd1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "There is still no solution to the diesel shortage",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Kumara Rajapaksa, President of the Petrol Station Owners Association, said today (26) in the morning that although the Petroleum Corporation has started fuel distribution, there is still a shortage of diesel.",
        "Mr. Rajapaksa said that the main reason for this situation is that the Petroleum Corporation provides more diesel to depots that are close to providing essential services. He also mentioned that if diesel is provided according to the code, buses can be directed to petrol stations."
      ],
